Use the standard library
This is how to fix_spaces of text:
  When isarray of text is yes, then:
    The answer is text
  End when
  Remember that result is ""
  Do this text's length times:
    Remember that ch is item 0 in text
    When ch is " ", then:
      Remember that result is "{result}_"
    But, if not:
      Remember that result is "{result}{ch}"
    End when
    Remember that text is item 1 in text
  End do
  The answer is result
